<Author>aristak
<Content>Excellent Service, Central Location We stayed at the Metropol for four days in April. The service and staff were absolutely excellent providing good advice on resturants, tour companies and more. They changed our room from interior to exterior (the front street was quiet) quite happily when we changed our mind. The hotel is located just two blocks from the very lovely and green Allemeda park and a 15 minute walk from the Zocalo. The hotel does not have air conditioning, so I could not say if it would be uncomfortable in the summer. A high quality tourist hotel! 
