<Content>Nice Hotel, Great travel office in hotel, GOOD prices We stayed at the Hotel Metropol in Mexico City. DF on the address is District Federal which you may see on many Mexico City addresses. The Hotel is verfy central and within walking distance of the main Zocoro (city center). The subway in Mexico City is only 20 cents ! which is 2 pesos, so don't be afraid to use it. Information in the subway has colorful maps. Wonderful Museums in the city especially at Chapultapec Park. Don't miss the Restaurant Havanna. Good food and great coffee. The Hotel Metropol has a full buffet breakfast, which is about $6 but worth it. Safe in the room, but you have to pay a deposit at the desk to get the key lock, and the money is returned at checkout. 
