<Content>Hotel Metropol was great! The Hotel Metropol was a great place to stay. Next time I am in Mexico city I plan to stay there again. Good for business travelers and people who are vaguely familiar with Mexico city. NOT good for students traveling alone as it is not near many eateries, stores etc. - is two subway (Metro) stops from the Zona Rosa, but is within 2 blocks walking distance to a subway station.Hovever, the service is great and the restaurant serves good food. The bar is ok - only one bartender - not many varieties, and imported liquor is very expensive as with all places in Mexico.Only a 5 block walk to the Palacio de Bellas Artes and a $20ish taxi ride from the bus station.I'd say it deserves 3 stars. 
